&lt;p id="cD4ojS"&gt;Here are the details that are currently available:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p id="ncWLAA"&gt;On October 30, 2024, a vulnerability was internally identified in generating the cache key for AD/LDAP DelAuth. The Bcrypt algorithm was...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
